      "content": "okay but my friend told me that dizziness and tremors together can actually be bad with lithium.. like toxicity? i'm kinda scared now. if i just stay home and follow what you said and i start feeling way worse, what's the actual sign that i'm in real danger and can't ignore it anymore?",
